These are Puzzles for 1x7 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-8-1::.
The people use 7 different means of transport: train, scooter, quad-bike, helicopter, taxi, tram, motorbike
 1. the person driving the train is somewhere to the right of the person driving the taxi##5
 2. the person driving the helicopter is somewhere between the person driving the tram and the person driving the taxi##7
 3. the person driving the scooter is somewhere between the person driving the tram and the person driving the train##7
 4. the person driving the scooter is somewhere to the left of the person driving the quad-bike##5
 5. the person driving the motorbike is not to the left of the person driving the tram##8
 6. the person driving the scooter is in an odd position##4
 7. the person driving the tram is on the left or right of the person driving the helicopter##3
 8. the person driving the tram is somewhere between the person driving the taxi and the person driving the motorbike##7
 9. the person driving the quad-bike is not to the right of the person driving the helicopter##8
10. the person driving the train is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |    3     |      4      |  5   |  6  |   7    |
| Transport   | taxi | train | scooter | quad-bike | helicopter | tram | motorbike |

