.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-8-2::.
The people use 7 different means of transport: quad-bike, skateboard, tram, helicopter, snowmobile, subway, trike
 1. the person driving the subway is the person driving the subway##1
 2. the person driving the tram is somewhere to the left of the person driving the quad-bike##5
 3. the person driving the subway is somewhere to the right of the person driving the skateboard##5
 4. the person driving the skateboard is in an even position##4
 5. the person driving the subway is on the left or right of the person driving the trike##3
 6. the person driving the helicopter is somewhere to the left of the person driving the skateboard##5
 7. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
 8. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
 9. the person driving the trike is in an even position##4
10. the person driving the snowmobile is not to the left of the person driving the quad-bike##8

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2     |    3     |     4      |       5       |    6     |      7       |
| Transport   | helicopter | skateboard | subway | trike | tram | quad-bike | snowmobile |

