.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-8-3::.
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: fonseca, havana, swisher, oliveros, cain, chaman, vegafina
 1. the oliveros-smoker is not to the left of the chaman-smoker##8
 2. the vegafina-smoker is in an even position##4
 3. the chaman-smoker is somewhere to the left of the havana-smoker##5
 4. the cain-smoker is on the left or right of the chaman-smoker##3
 5. the oliveros-smoker is on the left or right of the chaman-smoker##3
 6. the vegafina-smoker is not to the right of the fonseca-smoker##8
 7. the swisher-smoker is somewhere between the chaman-smoker and the havana-smoker##7
 8. the fonseca-smoker is in an odd position##4
 9. the fonseca-smoker is not to the right of the swisher-smoker##8
10. the chaman-smoker is on the right of the cain-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2    |     3      |      4      |   5   |    6    |    7    |
| Cigar   | cain | chaman | oliveros | vegafina | fonseca | swisher | havana |

