.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-8-4::.
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: november, october, july, september, january, august, december
 1. the person who's birthday is in november is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in july and the person who's birthday is in october##7
 2. the person who's birthday is in august is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in october##5
 3. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in january is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in december and the person who's birthday is in october##7
 5. the person who's birthday is in december is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in january and the person who's birthday is in september##7
 6. the person who's birthday is in september is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in november and the person who's birthday is in december##7
 7. the person who's birthday is in november is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in august##8
 8. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in december##3
 9. the person who's birthday is in december is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in september##8
10. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1   |  2  |   3   |    4     |   5   |   6    |  7   |
| Birthday   | july | november | september | december | january | october | august |

