 5. the person drinking sprite is somewhere to the right of the person drinking cola##5
 6. the person drinking soy-milk is somewhere to the left of the person drinking cola##5
 7. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
 8. the person drinking sprite is between the person drinking cola and the person drinking fanta##2
