10. the person drinking sprite is not to the left of the person drinking lemonade##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |   3    |   4    |     5     |    6     |     7     |
| Beverage   | lemonade | soy-milk | juice | hot-chocolate | cola | sprite | fanta |

